{"tid":1834393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強：721事件警隊有可以做得更好的地方","createTime":"2020-01-22T11:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T11:48:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"35a267af600373c3a1b208fdbc6706e8025ef125","tid":1834393,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"警務處處長鄧炳強出席荃灣區議會後被問到，在721事件中，黑衣人和白衣人的責任是否相同。鄧炳強說不論甚麼顏色衫的人，任何人只要犯法和使用暴力都會徹查，部分人已被捕或被控告，部分仍在調查中。他承認721事件中，警隊有可以做得更好的地方，否則不會出現如此多猜疑，會從做得不好的地方中學習。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人指控在荃灣警署內被強姦，鄧炳強早前表示，警方現正循誤導警員或給予假口供方向調查，代表律師其後發聲明指鄧炳強的言論損害當事人利益。鄧炳強回應，他所說的是事實陳述，事件牽涉重大的公眾利益，以及市民對警隊的信任情況，因此有需要回應。<br />\n<br />\n至於早前有警員在鏡頭前展示記者的身分證，鄧炳強認為相關行為並不恰當，已訓斥涉事的兩名警員，但並無回應會否對相關警員作進一步紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504229-20200122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504229-20200122.htm&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzbktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=db4bf2f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504229-20200122.htm&h=c1e7e082\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504229-20200122.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7a4ae1891b339d79a0e03ba9e2869d092da63b19","tid":1834393,"uid":31017,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"係元朗祠堂賽後檢討仲未傾夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9ff19efa69c686fd947329f0908f7c140767a7","tid":1834393,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"